356
00:18:35,679 --> 00:18:37,768
this man's been
in Lorna's corner.

357
00:18:37,812 --> 00:18:39,857
- Minus that six weeks
when she went solo.

358
00:18:39,901 --> 00:18:42,295
- That's just a bump
in the road, Chuck.

359
00:18:42,338 --> 00:18:44,862
