at the first sight of blood

362
00:18:49,606 --> 00:18:51,521
and try to stop the fight?

363
00:18:51,565 --> 00:18:53,523
- [Ringside Announcer]
We'll know soon enough.

364
00:18:53,567 --> 00:18:56,178
[bell dinging]

