00:22:43,057 --> 00:22:44,667
- You don't? Really?

463
00:22:44,711 --> 00:22:47,714
I apologize, how about that?

464
00:22:49,150 --> 00:22:51,718
- You are a grown woman.

465
00:22:51,761 --> 00:22:54,677
Whatever happened,
